    "Numerous CNN architectures have been suggested for plankton recognition.",
    "These include various common CNN developed for generic image recognition such as AlexNet (Krizhevsky et al. 2012), VGGNet (Simonyan and Zisserman 2014), GoogLeNet (Szegedy et al. 2015), and ResNet (He et al. 2016).",
